quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,33,"Mana obubii bwabakhola bwakhabaloleshele, ne kalibolela kalia akabakholelanga omubayo."
  45,34,"Baliboolelwa mbu: “Olwalelo khubebilila shingala enywe mwebilila omukhung’ano kweyinyanga yenyu ino. Eshimenyo shienyu nimumulilo, ne mubula babahabina."
  45,35,"Khulwo khuba enywe mwakholelanga tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye omubayo mana obulamu bwokhushialo nibubakatilisia.” Kholeelo shibalirusibwamwo tawe nohomba shibalileshelwa tawe."
  45,36,"Kho okhwitsomibwa nikhwa Nyasaye Omulesi we likulu, Omulesi weshialo, Omulesi webilonjo bioosi."
  45,37,"Ne obukhongo ni obubwe butswa yenyene, mwikulu nende khushialo, naye ni owa Amaani, Omuchesi muno."
  46,1,"Ha, Mim."
  46,2,"Okhwishibwa khweshitabu khurula khu Nyasaye owa Amaani, Omuchesi muno."
  46,3,"Shikhwaloonga likulu nende eshialo nende bioosi bili hakari wabio halali khubwatoto nende ebise biarebwaho. Ne balia bakhaya shibabukulanga oluchendo mukabekanyilisibungwa tawe."
  46,4,"Boola mbu: “Mulolangakhwo biamulamanga bilali Nyasaye, munzechesie ni shina shabialonga shili khushialo, nohomba bali nende obulala khu walonga likulu, mundererekhwo eshitabu eshialiho imbeli wa shino, nohomba eshimanyisio shiosishiosi shiobumanyi nikali mbu muboolanga obwatoto?”"
  46,5,"Ni omukori omukhongo uli arie ushilakhwo ulamaanga abalali Nyasaye tawe, abalalibafuchilila okhula inyanga yeyindukho tawe, nabo kata bakorerwe obusabi bwabu obo."